    "In contrast, combining both u-and g-band observations yields unbiased τDRW estimates down to hourly timescales.",
    "cleaning cuts used for EzTaoX, which remove about 5% of the JAVELIN fits.",
    "JAVELIN produces biased estimates of τ DRW from our simulated LSST WFD light curves.",
